<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-07 08:50:24 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<CATEGORY> financial </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Monday Gold Coin Prices  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
        NEW YORK (AP) -- Selected coin prices Monday  
</P>
<P>
                           Gold Coins    	
</P>
<P>
                                     Bid        Chg.
</P>
<P>
  American Eagle, 1 troy oz.        $280.40 up   $ 0.30
</P>
<P>
  American Eagle, .50 oz.           $142.10 up   $ 0.20
</P>
<P>
  American Eagle, .25 oz.           $72.40  up   $ 0.10
</P>
<P>
  American Eagle, .10 oz.           $30.50
</P>
<P>
  Austla. Kangaroo, 1 troy oz.      $278.20 up   $ 0.30
</P>
<P>
