<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  Rivers Will Coach Magic As He Played </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ORLANDO, Fla. (AP) -- Doc Rivers plans to coach the same way he  
played. 
</P>
<P>
