<HEADLINE>  Belgium Food Scandal Spreads </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BRUSSELS, Belgium (AP) -- The Belgian government added butter to  
its list of banned foods on Monday, denying residents another key 
ingredient in their already depleted diets after cancer-causing 
dioxins were found in Belgian foods. 
</P>
<P>
	Leaders huddled in crisis session for a fourth straight day,  
while hundreds of butcher and baker shops closed because the 
