<P>
	The government and leading opposition parties also agreed to set  
up a special inquiry commission to investigate how the 
cancer-causing dioxins ended up on Belgian dinner plates so easily. 
Dioxin is a byproduct of the manufacture of some herbicides and 
pesticides. 
