	Meanwhile, the police investigation into the scandal suffered a  
setback early Monday when a court ordered the release of the only 
two suspects in the case, Lucien and Jan Verkest, who run an animal 
feed-fat production company, saying there was insufficient evidence 
to hold them. However, the two were again remanded into custody 
later Monday after prosecutors appealed. 
</P>
