</P>
<P>
	Thailand banned meat, eggs and dairy products from Belgium, and  
Malaysia banned the same products from the European Union. 
Singapore suspended sales of all livestock and byproducts imported 
from any European country. 
</P>
<P>
	In Israel, Belgian products containing eggs, milk and meat were  
ordered to be removed from store shelves. 
</P>
<P>
	The scandal was also tearing at the center-left coalition ahead  
of Sunday's elections. The farm ministry has traditionally been a 
